OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mild night
OL,6,Fwith cloud thickening and bringing
OL,7,Foutbreaks of patchy light rain in
OL,8,Fplaces. This should largely clear
OL,9,Ftowards dawn, with some clearer spells
OL,10,Flikely to develop. Winds will remain
OL,11,Fgenerally light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FPatchy cloud to start will
OL,14,Fgive way to some sunny spells and
OL,15,Flight winds. Warm for most places, but
OL,16,Fa little cooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
